        <DisplayName>RaspberryDebugger</DisplayName>
        <Description xml:space="preserve">The Raspberry Debugger extension provides an easy way to debug your Raspberry .NET Core applications on a real Raspberry Pie using Visual Studio:

* Creates and manages your SSH keys transparently
* Handles installation of Windows OpenSSH
* Installs the target .NET SDK on your Raspberry
* Installs the remote VSDBG debugger
* F5 and go, we handle transferring app binaries and starting the debugger
* Compatible with .NET Core 3.1 (we'll support ,NET 5 when it's officially released)
* Manage connections to multiple Raspberries

Raspberry Debugger extension is compatible with Raspberry Pi
Raspberry Pi is a trademark of the Raspberry Pi Foundation</Description>
